lead_paragraph: Carlos Brathwaite smashed England's Ben Stokes for four successive sixes in the final over with a breathtaking display of power-hitting to snatch a sensational four-wicket victory for the West Indies in the World Twenty20 final on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Brathwaite's Four Sixes Seal Glorious Windies Triumph
